<item>
            <title>[DOXIA-323] Apt parser garbles some special characters inside tables</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DOXIA-323</link>
                <project id="12317230" key="DOXIA">Maven Doxia (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Apt snippet:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;  \~, \=, \-, \+, \*, \[, \], \&amp;lt;, \&amp;gt;, \{, \}, \\.

*---------------------------------------------+--------------+
| \~, \=, \-, \+, \*, \[, \], \&amp;lt;, \&amp;gt;, \{, \}, \\.     | Apt special characters
*---------------------------------------------+--------------+
| $\{JAVA_HOME\}                             | The JAVA_HOME environment value.
*---------------------------------------------+--------------+
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The characters &amp;lt;, &amp;gt;, &lt;/p&gt;
{, }
&lt;p&gt;, \ are not rendered inside the table. This worked in Doxia 1.0.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
