                            <comment id="14431782" author="ltheussl" created="Sun, 24 May 2009 00:52:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Vincent,&lt;br/&gt;
I think this has been introduced by your fixes for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DOXIA-38&quot; title=&quot;Independent row parsing&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DOXIA-38&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DOXIA-38&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DOXIA-134&quot; title=&quot;Apt parser issues&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DOXIA-134&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DOXIA-134&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. I have added a test case in AptParserTest.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14431699" author="siveton" created="Wed, 27 May 2009 05:01:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;FYI using double reverse solidus ie &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;\\&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; in a cell is incorrectly rendered with Doxia 1.0 (ie with maven-site-plugin:2.0): it becomes \240.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
